Born from a partnership between @JacobAndCo and the international graffiti artist Alek Monopoly, unboxing the all new “Monopoly” masterpiece in the Astronomia Grande Complication collection.

It features a flamboyant and varied color combination tipical of the pop art vision that define the character of the artist.

Inside the iconic domed rose gold case with its characteristic triple axis tourbillon architecture, all the characters and symbols of the contemporary artist are allocated, including "The Monopoly Man" and "Scrooge McDuck," a multicolored dollar sign with multiple drawings of diamonds, and "money wings."
The painting of the characters with acrylic colors on such a small scale was among the most challenging works of the prolific street artist
Limited Edition to just 9 pieces worldwide
⌚️tag price: $ 600,000.00

node.text:
The Sultan of Brunei, Hassanal Bolkiah known for collecting watches and has many piece uniques from serval brands has been celebrated his 75th birthday wearing the new “rare bird” Patek Philippe Nautilus 5711/1A-014 featuring a stainless steel case with the new green olive dial.
This particular watch has a list price of $ 34,800.00 but on the market you can find it for no less than $ 400,000.00.
•
📸 @bruneiroyalfamily | @vertigo1983

Hands on the @wristaficionado Richard Mille RM11-03 Automatic Flyback Chrono Red Quartz FQ TPT, a mixture of red quartz and carbon, produced in a series of layers (“TPT” is “thin-ply technology”) which offer an attractive aesthetic when machined. It also features a flyback-style chronograph with a 12-hour counter (hours and minutes are counted in the same dial), synchronized 60-minute countdown dial, and a big date indicator along with a month indicator neatly placed between 4 and 5 o’clock on the dial. 
One of the most sought discontinued Richard Mille actually on the market. Now available at @wristaficionado boutique 🇺🇸

The new @aventi A11-05 Emerald REC is something else🟩🔥
A mesmerizing and complicated timepiece that features a 68 facet case (a brilliant cut diamond has 58 facets) in a super cool material called Emerald REC.
The watch also features a dual barrel Flying tourbillon movement with 72h of power reserve. Everything is on display through the skeletonized dial 👌🏼
Limited Edition to 100 pieces worldwide 
⌚️tag price: $12,000.00

Wrist checking the all new @JacobAndCo Astronomia Casino Black Edition 🎰⚫️

Never before has there been a grand complication timepiece with a roulette wheel that spins, allowing owners to play their favorite game of chance at any time.

The Astronomia Casino's case measures 47 millimeters in diameter and 24 millimeters thick between the highest point of its specially domed front sapphire crystal and the lowest point of its case. Crafted from 18K black gold, the case features four sapphire crystal windows installed throughout the periphery, allowing for unhindered viewing of the spectacular double-axis tourbillon caliber and the functioning roulette wheel.� Keeping the theme, the roulette dial is crafted out of 18K black gold.
Limited Edition to just 9 pieces worldwide
⌚️tag price: $620,000.00
